commit.message: Refactored chart creation to strawman idiom

addon: directly fetch parameters from messages page instead of network requests
add public key into manifest to keep the extension id constant between debug and production
Card solid background, removed unused library
Zooming and panning added to sentiment chart (overhaul; very fast performance)
Scatterplot with sizing based on exchange length
More modelling with discrepency as the abs difference between adjacent exchanges
client: grab own user ID from __user
Changed to point client at server.
Added regex to detect and replace urls with space
server: split messages into sent and received
server: use data from analyser (using hardcoded dataset for now)
Interfaces with indico API testing against local static content.
